I can't wait, I'm looking
forward to the relaunch tonight.

38:51.734 --> 38:52.603
We're going to have a lot of fun.

38:52.603 --> 38:54.065
- You like it?

38:54.065 --> 38:55.108
- Thank you.
- Yeah?

38:55.108 --> 38:56.023
You like it?

38:56.023 --> 38:56.892
Good man.

39:00.118 --> 39:00.986
With the new decor,

39:00.986 --> 39:02.363
