39:02.363 --> 39:04.844
- Hello welcome to the River Rock,

39:04.844 --> 39:06.594
I'm Karen.

39:06.594 --> 39:07.597
- [Gordon] Along with
a newly inspired Ken.

39:07.597 --> 39:09.952
- Nice to see you, how you been?

39:09.952 --> 39:11.041
Enjoy your dinner.

39:11.041 --> 39:12.108
- Thank you.

39:12.108 --> 39:13.387
- [Gordon] The River Rock
is in a much better place.

39:14.451 --> 39:17.305
Time to go, when I got here Ken, honestly,

39:17.305 --> 39:18.983
