39:18.983 --> 39:20.485
Almost like someone had given up,

39:20.485 --> 39:22.813
but we've turned him around.

39:23.913 --> 39:26.095
It's almost like he's sort
of, he's got his mojo back

39:27.081 --> 39:29.838
and now River Rock has
every chance of succeeding.

39:29.838 --> 39:32.716
I tell you what, I've seen a lot of skies,

39:32.716 --> 39:35.604
