39:35.604 --> 39:36.473
Fuck me.

39:37.447 --> 39:40.515
As I prepare to leave, guests
are arriving for the relaunch

39:40.515 --> 39:44.254
and I noticed some familiar
faces from the bar last night

39:44.254 --> 39:45.260
