39:45.260 --> 39:46.953
- How are you my darling?

39:46.953 --> 39:48.498
- Nice to meet you.

39:48.498 --> 39:49.367
- She's going to meet Kenny tonight.

39:49.367 --> 39:51.971
- Oh you're the date.

39:51.971 --> 39:54.598
He's around, have a
peek, have a little peek.

39:54.598 --> 39:55.467
First impressions?

39:55.467 --> 39:56.975
- He looks cute.

39:56.975 --> 39:57.887
- Looks cute.

39:57.887 --> 39:58.756
Nice.

40:00.171 --> 40:02.531
I can feel a good night coming on.

40:02.531 --> 40:04.845
(women laughing)

40:04.845 --> 40:06.385
(dramatic music)

40:06.385 --> 40:08.846
- Joey I need three onion
soups, three fish cakes

40:08.846 --> 40:10.555
and fish fingers.

40:10.555 --> 40:11.759
- [Gordon] With Ken trusting his staff

40:11.759 --> 40:13.544
and not micromanaging, he's able to spend

40:13.544 --> 40:14.763
more time on the floor.

40:14.763 --> 40:15.632
- Salute my friends.

40:15.632 --> 40:18.566
- [Gordon] Leaving time to
charm the Milson Milford.

40:18.566 --> 40:19.669
- Hello, how's everyone tonight?

40:19.669 --> 40:21.300
Welcome.

40:21.300 --> 40:22.536
- And this is..

40:22.536 --> 40:25.369
- Hi Kenny, very nice to meet you.

40:25.369 --> 40:27.975
- Nice to meet you, follow me.

40:29.136 --> 40:31.066
- Come on wake up.

40:31.066 --> 40:34.476
- I was excited to see
them, she was very pretty.

40:34.476 --> 40:36.811
I look forward to talking with her.

40:36.811 --> 40:37.990
There we go ladies.

40:37.990 --> 40:39.711
- [Woman] Why thank you so much.

40:39.711 --> 40:41.007
- [Ken] Salute.

40:41.007 --> 40:43.096
- My first impressions
of Ken, he looks cute,

40:43.096 --> 40:44.138
very gentlemen like.

40:45.342 --> 40:46.893
See how the night goes.

40:46.893 --> 40:48.514
- Salute ladies, thank you very much.

40:52.160 --> 40:54.746
- The inn is buzzing and
Ken has invited some very

40:54.746 --> 40:57.144
special guests to see
the place at it's best.

40:57.144 --> 40:58.249
- And this is my brother.

40:58.249 --> 41:00.197
- Oh, how are you sir?

41:00.197 --> 41:01.252
- Pleased to meet you.

41:01.252 --> 41:02.121
- Likewise.

41:02.121 --> 41:02.990
Good to see you too.

41:02.990 --> 41:03.858
- And my mother.

41:03.858 --> 41:05.069
- Hello madame, how are you?

41:05.069 --> 41:05.937
- Hi, how are you?

41:05.937 --> 41:06.806
- Very well, thank you, nice to meet you.

41:06.806 --> 41:08.802
- There's no words to express,
how proud I am of Kenneth.

41:08.802 --> 41:10.418
- Upstairs, the guests are loving

41:10.418 --> 41:12.347
the new rooms and downstairs,

41:12.347 --> 41:14.797
they're loving the fresh
local menu that chef Seth

41:14.797 --> 41:16.776
and I put together.

41:16.776 --> 41:17.645
- Really really good.

41:17.645 --> 41:19.084
- Delicious.

41:19.084 --> 41:19.952
- It's really good.

41:22.044 --> 41:23.973
- Before I can leave,
there's one last thing

41:23.973 --> 41:25.751
I need to take care of.

41:25.751 --> 41:27.549
Can I have your cellular please?

41:27.549 --> 41:29.065
No not for me, for Ken come on.

41:32.096 --> 41:34.358
Amazing, hey listen thanks
so much for coming tonight.

41:34.358 --> 41:36.037
I really appreciate it.

41:36.037 --> 41:37.372
- [Woman] Thank you for asking.

41:37.372 --> 41:40.166
- Ken come here, now how are you feeling?

41:40.166 --> 41:41.365
- I feel wonderful.

41:41.365 --> 41:43.263
- When I saw you at the
beginning at the week

41:43.263 --> 41:44.191
I thought you were going to sort of almost

41:45.962 --> 41:47.159
I suppose fall to the wayside,

41:47.159 --> 41:48.185
but you bounced back and
I'm grateful for that.

41:48.185 --> 41:49.415
- Thank you, I'm grateful for you.

41:49.415 --> 41:50.719
- Oh, and one more thing.

41:53.199 --> 41:54.869
(Ken laughing)

41:54.869 --> 41:56.777
- Kim's cell number, it's for you.

41:57.949 --> 41:59.962
- You can't have a better
wing man than Gordon Ramsey,

41:59.962 --> 42:02.113
holy shit, he gave me her number,

42:02.113 --> 42:03.005
it's in my pocket.

42:08.526 --> 42:10.248
- No more sticky notes,
nothing, let them do it.

42:10.248 --> 42:11.823
- I will.
- Yeah?

42:11.823 --> 42:12.692
Okay.

42:14.117 --> 42:16.755
- Love you, I think you're the
greatest, thank you so much.

42:16.755 --> 42:19.289
Gordon made me realise that
I should be less of the

42:19.289 --> 42:22.584
hands-on owner who can't see
the forest through the trees,

42:22.584 --> 42:25.191
from here on I'm empowering my staff

42:25.191 --> 42:26.650
to make their own decisions

42:27.758 --> 42:28.955
and I'm going to support them,

42:28.955 --> 42:30.908
no more micromanaging for me.

42:32.562 --> 42:33.668
- What a week.

42:33.668 --> 42:34.724
What a galaxy.

42:35.680 --> 42:36.549
Fuck me.
